sult X. The assignment vectors from the R1TA power iteration layer are reshaped back to their matrix form such that X(k) = (x(ikkâˆ’) 1ik ) âˆˆ RIkâˆ’1Ã—Ik . Then, the 1 normalization is performed row and column alternatively through multiple
iterations. Forward pass. For each pair of iterations, we start from row normalization. In the (n + 1) and (n + 2)-th iteration:

