6. Conclusion
In this paper we proposed a novel deep architecture for MOT, which learns jointly, in an end-to-end fashion, features and high-order afï¬nity directly from the ground truth trajectories. During tracking, predictions from SOT and a dedicated target management are include to further boost tracking robustness. Experiments on the MOT2015, MOT2017, KITTI-Car and UA-DETRAC datasets clearly show the effectiveness of proposed approach.

